{"tid":2478143,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本計畫宮崎部署F-35B戰機 加強離島防衛","createTime":"2021-04-06T22:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-06T23:42:15.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3b33330f645f59c73c841b093f9c744ea19c40cd","tid":2478143,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T22:49:53.000Z","msg":"日本計畫宮崎部署F-35B戰機 加強離島防衛<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/2040153/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F2040153%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtGt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=552d172c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F2040153%2F&h=b14c923c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/2040153/</a><br />\n<br />\n日本傳媒報道，防衛省計畫在位於九州島的宮崎縣航空自衛隊新田原基地部署F-35B戰機，加強離島防衛。<br />\n<br />\n《讀賣新聞》引述一名防衛省官員指，日方將F-35B定位為「離島防衛的王牌」，F-35B是短距起飛、垂直降落型戰機，即使在無基地的離島，亦可以靈活利用民用機場升降。F-35B部署到新田原基地後，將可以直飛釣魚島附近空域，未來亦可能與準航母級別的加賀號兩棲攻擊艦，展開共同訓練。 <br />\n<br />\n日本打算購買42架這型戰機，在2023財政年度前購買18架。另外，日本打算最終部署105架常規起降型F-35A戰機，一些這型戰機已經服役，部署在東北部青森縣的基地。"},{"pid":"35ee17102601da9e69d0cb8b94d1900500329ee2","tid":2478143,"uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T22:52:07.000Z","msg":"宮崎😍😍😍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYHWGBtkSBTk5quGaV4QQjV5bHDDeBqQoUTcrU152NXXZ?filename=oetYpyF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoetYpyF.png&h=80b28c02&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2785e4b958f3b0c204db9d2fafc3a10e70bc28e8","tid":2478143,"uid":168384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T22:57:16.000Z","msg":"宮崎駿😍😍😍<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.gstatic.com/tv/thumb/persons/156932/156932_v9_ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gstatic.com%2Ftv%2Fthumb%2Fpersons%2F156932%2F156932_v9_ba.jpg&h=0abeb6f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87977af2dfc943630d9df0bce5356fb0f11421a4","tid":2478143,"uid":177590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35ee17102601da9e69d0cb8b94d1900500329ee2","tid":2478143,"uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T22:52:07.000Z","msg":"宮崎😍😍😍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oetYpyF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoetYpyF.png&h=80b28c02&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T23:40:30.000Z","msg":"青島神社<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ae6b5e4bc942dc29be05b07c1152ce2a77251e","tid":2478143,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87977af2dfc943630d9df0bce5356fb0f11421a4","tid":2478143,"uid":177590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35ee17102601da9e69d0cb8b94d1900500329ee2","tid":2478143,"uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T22:52:07.000Z","msg":"宮崎😍😍😍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oetYpyF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoetYpyF.png&h=80b28c02&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T23:40:30.000Z","msg":"青島神社<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T23:42:15.000Z","msg":"宮崎囡囡😍😍😍😍😍😍"}]}